1
00:00:04,220 --> 00:00:07,260
" Princess Silver "

2
00:00:07,500 --> 00:00:09,820
Episode 41

3
00:00:10,660 --> 00:00:13,460
Lady Fu refuses to live in
the palace for recovery.

4
00:00:13,620 --> 00:00:15,780
She insists to stay
in the Cold Palace.

5
00:00:17,500 --> 00:00:18,740
Was it Senyan Palace?

6
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:22,460
Yes, I tried talking to her.
But she refuses to leave.

7
00:00:22,620 --> 00:00:26,060
So I ordered my men
to renovate Senyan Palace.

8
00:00:26,900 --> 00:00:29,420
Right, any reports
from the south fringe?

9
00:00:29,660 --> 00:00:31,860
Southern fringe is
carrying out a new policy.

10
00:00:32,020 --> 00:00:34,300
It has shown result
for the past one year.

11
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:36,140
Qin Yong?

12
00:00:36,900 --> 00:00:40,100
Back then, Qin Yong was able to carry
out the people-based transformation...

13
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:42,900
because of Lady Yun's help.

14
00:00:44,180 --> 00:00:46,260
It enabled Northern Realm
to build up strong army...

15
00:00:46,420 --> 00:00:49,420
and enrich the people in a very short
time after we recovered from war...

16
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:51,180
to become a force itself.

17
00:00:51,540 --> 00:00:54,020
Too bad Qin Yong lack judgement.

18
00:00:54,180 --> 00:00:56,180
That's why his
people-based transformation...

19
00:00:56,380 --> 00:00:57,780
had failed in the end.

20
00:00:59,660 --> 00:01:01,860
Your Highness, this new policy...

21
00:01:02,060 --> 00:01:03,740
is carried out together by...

22
00:01:03,940 --> 00:01:06,100
Prince Li and that consort of his.

23
00:01:07,580 --> 00:01:08,620
Her?

24
00:01:12,740 --> 00:01:14,420
Any other news?

25
00:01:14,860 --> 00:01:16,260
We have a secret message
from Qingzhou.

26
00:01:16,420 --> 00:01:18,780
It is said that recently,
there are some rumours in the city.

27
00:01:18,980 --> 00:01:20,740
It's rumoured that...

28
00:01:21,140 --> 00:01:23,020
there's a Silver-Hair Demon.

29
00:01:23,180 --> 00:01:24,580
What Silver-Hair Demon?

30
00:01:25,060 --> 00:01:27,700
They say that the consort
is a Silver-Hair Demon.

31
00:01:28,220 --> 00:01:29,740
Some said that this consort...

32
00:01:29,860 --> 00:01:31,900
used the be a general's wife
in Northern Realm.

33
00:01:32,100 --> 00:01:33,620
They said that she's a wanton...

34
00:01:33,780 --> 00:01:36,020
and had eloped with
Prince Li to the southern fringe.

35
00:01:36,220 --> 00:01:39,140
This rumour has spread
like a wild fire in that city.

36
00:01:40,180 --> 00:01:43,140
Pass down my order.
Find the source of the rumour.

37
00:01:44,540 --> 00:01:46,580
Yes, I understand.

38
00:01:47,300 --> 00:01:49,460
-Follow me to Senyan Palace.
-Yes, Your Highness.

39
00:02:06,460 --> 00:02:07,500
Mother.

40
00:02:09,740 --> 00:02:10,980
Chou.

41
00:02:12,580 --> 00:02:13,940
Greetings, mother.

42
00:02:14,900 --> 00:02:17,340
Chou. Finally, you are back.

43
00:02:17,580 --> 00:02:18,620
Mother.

44
00:02:18,820 --> 00:02:21,260
I had been engaging in war
for the past one year.

45
00:02:21,380 --> 00:02:24,380
Please don't blame me for not being
able to take care of you by my side.

46
00:02:28,900 --> 00:02:32,220
Look at you. You've been
separated from me for so long...

47
00:02:32,380 --> 00:02:34,260
until we are so estranged.

48
00:02:34,540 --> 00:02:35,980
That's not true.

49
00:02:36,660 --> 00:02:38,780
I'm gratified that you are putting...

50
00:02:38,980 --> 00:02:40,660
the country before you.

51
00:02:40,940 --> 00:02:43,060
-Why would I blame you?
-Yes, mother.

52
00:02:43,780 --> 00:02:46,220
Your Majesty, food is ready.

53
00:02:46,580 --> 00:02:48,420
Come. Let's eat.

54
00:02:50,740 --> 00:02:51,860
After you, mother.

55
00:03:02,740 --> 00:03:04,300
I remember that when I was young,

56
00:03:05,340 --> 00:03:06,460
you...

57
00:03:07,060 --> 00:03:09,620
were always so distant and cold.

58
00:03:10,020 --> 00:03:11,740
And you never ate with me.

59
00:03:13,020 --> 00:03:15,180
Actually,
I only understood later on...

60
00:03:16,260 --> 00:03:19,580
that you were leaving me
with all the good food...

61
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:23,100
while you sat aside to eat
those leftovers in secret.

62
00:03:24,620 --> 00:03:25,900
Unfortunately,

63
00:03:27,580 --> 00:03:29,580
I still don't have a way...

64
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:31,180
to hold a feast for you.

65
00:03:31,740 --> 00:03:33,100
But don't worry, mother.

66
00:03:33,340 --> 00:03:36,700
I'll hold a coronation ceremony
for you in a few days' time...

67
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:38,340
to welcome you back to the court.

68
00:03:40,140 --> 00:03:41,980
It's all because of my mental illness.

69
00:03:42,900 --> 00:03:45,900
Fortunately I've recovered now.

70
00:03:46,180 --> 00:03:48,300
I won't drag you down
that much anymore.

71
00:03:48,540 --> 00:03:50,580
What are you talking about?

72
00:03:51,180 --> 00:03:53,140
We've been through life and death
to be together.

73
00:03:53,260 --> 00:03:55,100
I'll fulfil my duty well as your son.

74
00:03:56,500 --> 00:03:59,420
Where have you been
for the past one year?

75
00:03:59,940 --> 00:04:01,860
You never came back to Zhongshan.

76
00:04:02,180 --> 00:04:05,580
You know how worried I am towards you?

77
00:04:06,140 --> 00:04:07,300
I know.

78
00:04:08,100 --> 00:04:10,340
For the past one year,
I had been travelling north.

79
00:04:10,580 --> 00:04:13,180
I had reclaimed the lands
that were taken away...

80
00:04:13,340 --> 00:04:14,860
by Wei one year ago.

81
00:04:15,700 --> 00:04:16,900
North?

82
00:04:17,980 --> 00:04:20,260
Why don't you go south?

83
00:04:21,780 --> 00:04:23,740
Do you mean the southern fringe?

84
00:04:26,260 --> 00:04:27,700
As for southern fringe,

85
00:04:28,340 --> 00:04:30,380
it is guarded by Zongzheng Wu You's
highly organised army.

86
00:04:30,620 --> 00:04:32,660
We can't underestimate their strength.

87
00:04:33,140 --> 00:04:35,580
I had sent some shock troops
to southern fringe before.

88
00:04:35,700 --> 00:04:37,540
But they were annihilated.

89
00:04:38,060 --> 00:04:41,220
My thought is, before I can
be sure of my enemy's strength,

90
00:04:41,740 --> 00:04:43,340
I won't act recklessly.

91
00:04:43,580 --> 00:04:44,980
I need to observe them first.

92
00:04:45,660 --> 00:04:48,060
If I were you,

93
00:04:48,860 --> 00:04:51,020
I'll send forth a fleet
to defeat them...

94
00:04:51,180 --> 00:04:53,820
once and for all before
they become fully fledged.

95
00:04:56,340 --> 00:04:58,660
But this is just
an opinion of a woman.

96
00:04:58,860 --> 00:05:01,140
You can just listen
and forget about it.

97
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:03,180
You are worried about the country too.

98
00:05:03,300 --> 00:05:04,580
I understand.

99
00:05:06,100 --> 00:05:07,460
Serve the wine.

100
00:05:13,500 --> 00:05:15,500
-Mother.
-Wench!

101
00:05:15,620 --> 00:05:17,820
-I'm going to kill you.
-Mother.

102
00:05:18,020 --> 00:05:19,380
I'm going to burn you to death.

103
00:05:19,540 --> 00:05:22,100
Look at your face scar.
I'm going to burn you to death.

104
00:05:22,220 --> 00:05:23,860
-Please spare my life!
-Mother.

105
00:05:24,020 --> 00:05:25,420
-I'll burn you to death!
-Mother!

106
00:05:25,540 --> 00:05:27,180
-Spare my life!
-I'll burn you to death.

107
00:05:27,340 --> 00:05:29,260
-I'll burn you to death!
-Mother!

108
00:05:29,820 --> 00:05:31,940
Don't just stand there!
Take her away! Quick!

109
00:05:32,620 --> 00:05:33,820
Quick.

110
00:05:34,260 --> 00:05:36,060
It's alright now, mother.

111
00:05:36,260 --> 00:05:38,220
-Ask them to stop. Don't burn me.
-Mother.

112
00:05:38,420 --> 00:05:41,940
-Don't burn me! Ask them to stop!
-It's alright now.

113
00:05:43,460 --> 00:05:45,260
-It's alright now, mother.
-Don't burn me.

114
00:05:45,460 --> 00:05:47,860
-Don't hit me.
-I'm in control of this palace now.

115
00:05:48,460 --> 00:05:50,980
Nobody will hurt you.
Don't be scared.

116
00:05:51,260 --> 00:05:53,820
Don't be scared.
It's fine now.

117
00:05:54,300 --> 00:05:56,060
-Don't hit me.
-It's fine now.

118
00:06:26,140 --> 00:06:28,980
Today is such a wonderful day.

119
00:06:29,180 --> 00:06:32,060
If it wasn't for the celebratory wine
bestowed by His Highness upon us,

120
00:06:32,180 --> 00:06:34,620
I would have been sober
for more than half a year.

121
00:06:35,540 --> 00:06:37,460
Brother. Let's drink till we drop.

122
00:06:37,580 --> 00:06:38,620
Alright!

123
00:06:43,380 --> 00:06:44,860
Did you see that?

124
00:06:45,220 --> 00:06:46,460
Silver-Hair Demon!

125
00:06:46,700 --> 00:06:49,740
You are drunk.
You must have seen it wrongly.

126
00:06:50,100 --> 00:06:53,900
That's right.
That is General Luo Qiao's tent.

127
00:06:54,260 --> 00:06:56,060
He is a bold and powerful man.

128
00:06:56,220 --> 00:06:58,820
No demon will dare get close to him.

129
00:06:59,020 --> 00:07:01,060
Let's take a look anyway.

130
00:07:01,500 --> 00:07:03,500
-Let's go then.
-Let's go.

131
00:07:07,540 --> 00:07:08,940
This...

132
00:07:14,100 --> 00:07:16,380
-General Luo Qiao!
-General Luo.

133
00:07:16,740 --> 00:07:18,700
-General Luo!
-There, look!

134
00:07:19,540 --> 00:07:21,860
Silver hair.
It's the Silver-Hair Demon!

135
00:07:22,020 --> 00:07:24,020
The Silver-Hair Demon
has killed General Luo.

136
00:07:25,540 --> 00:07:27,980
Your Highness, this is the
overall situation of the incident.

137
00:07:28,740 --> 00:07:30,580
The three soldiers who had
discovered the body first hand...

138
00:07:30,700 --> 00:07:32,060
are now under supervision.

139
00:07:32,260 --> 00:07:34,900
They just had a fleeting glimpse
of a person with silver hair.

140
00:07:35,060 --> 00:07:37,340
But it's possible that they saw
wrongly because they are drunk.

141
00:07:38,620 --> 00:07:41,300
Question them carefully.
We can't miss out on any details.

142
00:07:41,700 --> 00:07:42,940
But most importantly,

143
00:07:43,100 --> 00:07:45,740
we can't let this news spread
and create further panic.

144
00:07:46,020 --> 00:07:47,900
Luo Army has always been very strict.

145
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:50,260
They had blocked the news
from spreading at once.

146
00:07:50,500 --> 00:07:52,660
But tonight is a special night.

147
00:07:52,820 --> 00:07:55,060
Many of them were drunk
in the celebratory feast.

148
00:07:55,300 --> 00:07:57,420
We can't be sure that
the news won't leak.

149
00:08:01,140 --> 00:08:02,660
This is indeed a sticky business.

150
00:08:04,140 --> 00:08:05,940
The one who created the rumour...

151
00:08:06,380 --> 00:08:08,860
seems to know us like
the back of his hand.

152
00:08:09,060 --> 00:08:10,460
He acts very cautiously...

153
00:08:10,740 --> 00:08:12,660
and leaves no trail behind.

154
00:08:13,220 --> 00:08:16,060
The scariest part is,
he is quite the schemer.

155
00:08:16,500 --> 00:08:19,980
He knows that he can
manipulate the people...

156
00:08:20,460 --> 00:08:22,180
through rumours and mystery.

157
00:08:22,340 --> 00:08:23,540
Your Highness.

158
00:08:25,860 --> 00:08:28,900
-Please back me up, Your Highness!
-General, don't be rude.

159
00:08:29,100 --> 00:08:31,460
General Luo Qiao is
a close brother of yours.

160
00:08:31,620 --> 00:08:34,300
That's why His Highness has been
investigating on it all night long.

161
00:08:34,460 --> 00:08:36,180
But we can't just look at
one side of the story.

162
00:08:36,300 --> 00:08:37,940
Lady Rong Le is with
His Highness for the whole night.

163
00:08:38,100 --> 00:08:39,460
Please give us the order...

164
00:08:39,660 --> 00:08:43,020
so that Luo Army can depart
immediately to the border.

165
00:08:44,300 --> 00:08:46,540
What is your purpose for doing so?

166
00:08:46,940 --> 00:08:48,260
I know clearly that...

167
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:51,140
the death of my brother is done
by someone with ulterior motive.

168
00:08:51,300 --> 00:08:55,180
His aim is to use my brother's life
to make us waver, to threaten you...

169
00:08:55,460 --> 00:08:57,180
and to put the blame
on Lady Rong Le.

170
00:08:57,660 --> 00:09:00,260
If we continue to stay
at the outskirts of Qingzhou,

171
00:09:00,420 --> 00:09:03,740
this case will be out in the open
tomorrow morning. Everybody will know.

172
00:09:03,900 --> 00:09:05,380
This will affect the people's loyalty.

173
00:09:05,620 --> 00:09:07,460
Although my brother's life
is important,

174
00:09:08,540 --> 00:09:10,460
we can't ruin the reputation of...

175
00:09:10,780 --> 00:09:12,340
Your Highness and Lady Rong Le.

176
00:09:14,060 --> 00:09:16,540
You believe in Lady Rong Le?

177
00:09:17,060 --> 00:09:18,100
Yes.

178
00:09:19,220 --> 00:09:21,100
If she is in a killing rage
and blood-lust,

179
00:09:21,300 --> 00:09:23,940
there will be no survivor
in this manor.

180
00:09:24,060 --> 00:09:26,300
Moreover, when I met her that day,

181
00:09:26,460 --> 00:09:29,300
although her hair is silver,
she still looks like a normal person.

182
00:09:29,660 --> 00:09:31,620
But she is willing to
stay inside this manor...

183
00:09:31,780 --> 00:09:33,660
because she doesn't want
to startle the people.

184
00:09:33,780 --> 00:09:37,180
Such a kind person like her
won't commit murder.

185
00:09:48,020 --> 00:09:49,220
Please rise.

186
00:09:52,260 --> 00:09:54,580
The man who planned this
is unfathomable.

187
00:09:54,740 --> 00:09:56,100
Whether you leave or not,

188
00:09:56,620 --> 00:09:59,300
I'm sure that this will only
get worse and worse.

189
00:09:59,620 --> 00:10:02,900
So, the thing that you should do
is not to run away with your soldiers.

190
00:10:03,860 --> 00:10:05,780
You have to use your reputation...

191
00:10:06,260 --> 00:10:07,860
reassure your soldiers.

192
00:10:08,980 --> 00:10:11,020
You've won victories
after victories in the battlefield.

193
00:10:11,260 --> 00:10:13,940
Are you going to lose
to this kind of evil plot?

194
00:10:14,580 --> 00:10:16,140
You believe in Lady Rong Le.

195
00:10:16,260 --> 00:10:18,620
I hope that you can believe in me too.

196
00:10:19,260 --> 00:10:22,300
I won't let General Luo Qiao
die in vain.

197
00:10:24,580 --> 00:10:25,700
Yes, Your Highness.

198
00:10:25,980 --> 00:10:28,260
Thank you for your teachings.

199
00:10:28,700 --> 00:10:30,980
I'll go back to the military camp now
to order them...

200
00:10:31,140 --> 00:10:33,780
to stay on high alert and
gather any evidences that I can.

201
00:10:40,660 --> 00:10:41,940
Leng Yan.

202
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:45,340
The Serene Hill Inn that
I had asked you to seal up,

203
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:46,700
unseal it immediately.

204
00:10:46,940 --> 00:10:48,340
Restore everything to normal.

205
00:10:48,500 --> 00:10:50,260
Just like nothing had ever happened.

206
00:10:50,420 --> 00:10:52,220
Are you trying to lure them out?

207
00:10:54,540 --> 00:10:57,820
The murdering schemers
are trying to create panic.

208
00:10:58,420 --> 00:11:00,140
But if everything has
gone back to normal,

209
00:11:00,380 --> 00:11:02,420
they will be the one panicking.

210
00:11:03,380 --> 00:11:05,180
Now, we don't have any evidence.

211
00:11:05,500 --> 00:11:07,140
But when the time comes,

212
00:11:08,060 --> 00:11:10,300
they might show their flaws.

213
00:11:11,100 --> 00:11:12,220
Yes, Your Highness.

214
00:11:21,620 --> 00:11:22,620
Sir Sun.

215
00:11:22,780 --> 00:11:25,420
Now, His Highness is
very cautious towards us...

216
00:11:25,580 --> 00:11:26,780
aristocratic clans.

217
00:11:26,940 --> 00:11:29,820
Is it safe for us to meet
each other in your manor?

218
00:11:30,020 --> 00:11:31,980
No need to panic.

219
00:11:32,220 --> 00:11:34,460
Come, sit down and have some tea.

220
00:11:36,900 --> 00:11:39,020
If you are not guilty,

221
00:11:39,580 --> 00:11:41,340
then you have nothing to be afraid of.

222
00:11:41,580 --> 00:11:42,900
But Sir Sun,

223
00:11:43,020 --> 00:11:46,900
I think His Highness has found out
that I embezzled the military funds.

224
00:11:47,140 --> 00:11:49,540
Although Prince Chen
didn't point me out in the court,

225
00:11:49,700 --> 00:11:52,860
his warning was bright and clear.

226
00:11:53,380 --> 00:11:56,260
Do we have a whistle-blower
in the court?

227
00:11:56,620 --> 00:11:59,300
I had already warned you not to be
too greedy in the first place...

228
00:11:59,460 --> 00:12:01,260
so that you won't end up
like Zheng family.

229
00:12:02,060 --> 00:12:04,100
But have you ever listened to me?

230
00:12:04,620 --> 00:12:06,220
Luo Zhi is back in the court now.

231
00:12:06,500 --> 00:12:07,980
His Highness has increased...

232
00:12:08,140 --> 00:12:10,980
his effort in suppressing
us scholars with the poor.

233
00:12:11,180 --> 00:12:14,260
It's possible that
he'll punish Cai family...

234
00:12:14,700 --> 00:12:16,540
as an example to others.

235
00:12:20,020 --> 00:12:21,420
I've regretted my doings.

236
00:12:21,580 --> 00:12:24,260
Given that we are both
prominent clans in Qingzhou...

237
00:12:24,460 --> 00:12:25,860
and we are old family friends,

238
00:12:25,940 --> 00:12:28,380
please save me and my family.

239
00:12:29,020 --> 00:12:31,220
You have exaggerated.

240
00:12:31,740 --> 00:12:32,780
Here.

241
00:12:36,100 --> 00:12:38,180
Sir Sun, save me.

242
00:12:39,660 --> 00:12:40,700
Sir Cai.

243
00:12:40,900 --> 00:12:44,060
Have you heard about
a rumour lately among the people...

244
00:12:44,260 --> 00:12:45,980
saying that a Silver-Hair Demon had...

245
00:12:46,140 --> 00:12:48,300
bring calamity to the country
and had seduced the prince?

246
00:12:49,460 --> 00:12:51,100
Are you saying that...

247
00:12:51,700 --> 00:12:53,540
I didn't say anything.

248
00:12:53,900 --> 00:12:57,220
But if you are smart,

249
00:12:57,700 --> 00:13:00,420
you should know what you have to do.

250
00:13:02,860 --> 00:13:04,500
Please give this to Miss Ling Yue.

251
00:13:04,820 --> 00:13:08,020
Miss Sun. Why don't you
give it to His Highness yourself?

252
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:10,140
If I give this to Sister Ling Yue,

253
00:13:10,300 --> 00:13:12,580
she will think that it's
for Lady Rong Le.

254
00:13:12,780 --> 00:13:14,140
What nonsense are you talking about?

255
00:13:14,260 --> 00:13:15,820
It makes no difference
