So, Lady Fu had kicked and hit her.

512
00:28:21,420 --> 00:28:23,940
And after that, she went missing.

513
00:28:24,100 --> 00:28:25,940
If I want to save her,

514
00:28:26,500 --> 00:28:29,140
I'm afraid that you are the
only one who can do that.

515
00:28:29,940 --> 00:28:31,380
I heard that...

516
00:28:31,620 --> 00:28:34,540
Prince Regent is going to enthroned
Lady Fu as empress dowager.

517
00:28:37,300 --> 00:28:38,540
What?

518
00:28:41,580 --> 00:28:42,820
Empress dowager?

519
00:28:43,540 --> 00:28:45,300
-Yes.
-You said that...

520
00:28:46,300 --> 00:28:48,260
he's going to enthrone her
as empress dowager?

521
00:28:48,540 --> 00:28:51,420
Yes. Prince Regent said that
she has recovered.

522
00:28:55,220 --> 00:28:57,180
She has recovered?

523
00:29:00,340 --> 00:29:01,780
Then, has she regained...

524
00:29:01,940 --> 00:29:03,980
all of her memories in the past?

525
00:29:04,780 --> 00:29:06,540
She is going to be
empress dowager now.

526
00:29:09,380 --> 00:29:10,900
I'm the empress.

527
00:29:11,420 --> 00:29:13,060
I've taken her place.

528
00:29:14,020 --> 00:29:16,180
She won't let go of me.

529
00:29:16,580 --> 00:29:19,420
Your Majesty, no matter what,
you are the previous empress.

530
00:29:19,860 --> 00:29:21,780
Fu Yuan is just a woman who has
just recovered from insanity.

531
00:29:21,980 --> 00:29:23,620
She won't be a threat to you.

532
00:29:23,740 --> 00:29:24,940
And there's Prince Regent.

533
00:29:25,140 --> 00:29:27,460
He has always been
respectful towards you, right?

534
00:29:30,420 --> 00:29:32,180
People like you...

535
00:29:32,420 --> 00:29:33,900
know nothing.

536
00:29:34,740 --> 00:29:35,820
-Your Majesty.
-Do you know...

537
00:29:35,940 --> 00:29:37,980
what kind of a person Fu Yuan is?

538
00:29:38,940 --> 00:29:40,820
She came back from hell.

539
00:29:40,940 --> 00:29:42,900
She is just like the demon itself!

540
00:29:44,460 --> 00:29:46,540
-Your Majesty.
-She's here to take our lives.

541
00:29:46,660 --> 00:29:49,820
-What's wrong with you, Your Majesty?
-She's here to take our lives!

542
00:29:51,180 --> 00:29:53,340
-Your Majesty!
-Go out.

543
00:29:54,540 --> 00:29:57,020
Go out! Go out now!

544
00:30:09,780 --> 00:30:11,500
Please save me.

545
00:30:13,580 --> 00:30:15,300
All these years,

546
00:30:17,460 --> 00:30:19,460
I've been putting
my pride in my pocket.

547
00:30:20,140 --> 00:30:21,940
I've never fought for anything.

548
00:30:22,820 --> 00:30:25,220
It's all because of self-preservation.

549
00:30:26,300 --> 00:30:29,540
I've dedicated my whole life
to this palace.

550
00:30:30,060 --> 00:30:32,100
I've dedicated myself to His Majesty.

551
00:30:33,340 --> 00:30:34,780
But now,

552
00:30:35,140 --> 00:30:36,860
His Majesty is dead.

553
00:30:37,500 --> 00:30:38,980
Crown prince is dead.

554
00:30:40,460 --> 00:30:42,100
Wu You has left.

555
00:30:43,620 --> 00:30:47,460
The people who I can rely on
in the past are gone.

556
00:30:47,580 --> 00:30:49,220
I can't rely on them anymore.

557
00:30:50,700 --> 00:30:52,020
Now,

558
00:30:53,500 --> 00:30:55,380
Fu Yuan is back.

559
00:30:55,740 --> 00:30:57,180
When she comes back,

560
00:31:00,060 --> 00:31:02,180
she won't let go of me.

561
00:31:04,380 --> 00:31:07,020
She'll make me wish that I'm dead.

562
00:31:15,020 --> 00:31:16,980
Why?

563
00:31:17,940 --> 00:31:20,580
Just like Sister Yun,

564
00:31:22,020 --> 00:31:25,460
we've never wanted to hurt anybody!

565
00:31:26,500 --> 00:31:28,460
I'm a devoted believer,

566
00:31:28,780 --> 00:31:30,620
a loyal servant to Buddha.

567
00:31:30,820 --> 00:31:33,060
Why are you treating me like this?

568
00:31:33,340 --> 00:31:36,220
Why did you put me
in such a sorry state?

569
00:31:36,380 --> 00:31:38,260
Why?

570
00:31:40,420 --> 00:31:43,660
This is so unfair!

571
00:31:55,940 --> 00:31:58,860
Why would the late empress
pass away suddenly?

572
00:31:59,380 --> 00:32:01,540
There are rumours from
the harem saying that...

573
00:32:01,740 --> 00:32:03,540
she didn't die from illness.

574
00:32:03,740 --> 00:32:05,460
They say that she hanged herself.

575
00:32:05,620 --> 00:32:07,860
The maidservants found out about it
when they brought her dinner.

576
00:32:07,980 --> 00:32:08,980
Impossible.

577
00:32:09,180 --> 00:32:11,860
The late empress
is from a clan of scholar.

578
00:32:11,980 --> 00:32:14,900
She has always been smart, cautious
and has taken care of herself well.

579
00:32:15,060 --> 00:32:16,300
-That's right.
-Even Prince Regent...

580
00:32:16,420 --> 00:32:17,980
has treated her with courtesy.

581
00:32:18,140 --> 00:32:20,220
Why would she commit suicide?

582
00:32:20,420 --> 00:32:21,540
That's right.

583
00:32:21,700 --> 00:32:24,140
Arrival of His Highness!

584
00:32:28,180 --> 00:32:31,020
Greetings, Your Highness.

585
00:32:43,780 --> 00:32:44,820
Please rise.

586
00:32:44,980 --> 00:32:47,260
Thank you, Your Highness.

587
00:32:49,020 --> 00:32:51,620
All of you here are
the pillars of the country.

588
00:32:51,820 --> 00:32:54,260
I've summoned you here today...

589
00:32:54,460 --> 00:32:55,900
because of one thing.

590
00:32:56,140 --> 00:32:58,580
I want to enthrone Empress Fu
as empress dowager.

591
00:32:58,740 --> 00:33:00,260
I want to give her back the
Golden Scroll and Phoenix Seal...

592
00:33:00,420 --> 00:33:01,940
and bring her back to
the ancestral temple.

593
00:33:02,060 --> 00:33:03,300
As for the details,

594
00:33:03,420 --> 00:33:06,340
I can only decide after
I've discussed with all of you.

595
00:33:06,500 --> 00:33:08,180
-This...
-This...

596
00:33:10,060 --> 00:33:11,820
From the way you look,

597
00:33:12,500 --> 00:33:14,260
is there any objection?

598
00:33:17,740 --> 00:33:21,060
Your Highness, the late empress
had just passed away yesterday.

599
00:33:21,220 --> 00:33:23,180
If we are so quick to enthrone
the empress dowager,

600
00:33:23,340 --> 00:33:25,860
-I'm afraid that it's unacceptable.
-Why is it unacceptable?

601
00:33:26,180 --> 00:33:28,700
She has just passed away and the truth
behind her death is still uncertain.

602
00:33:28,860 --> 00:33:30,540
The late empress has fallen ill...

603
00:33:30,700 --> 00:33:33,620
because she misses the late emperor
until the illness has taken her away.

604
00:33:33,940 --> 00:33:37,100
Now, the late empress is
together with the late emperor.

605
00:33:37,260 --> 00:33:39,260
What truth do we need
to be certain about?

606
00:33:39,620 --> 00:33:42,540
Please be rest assured.
I'll take care of...

607
00:33:42,900 --> 00:33:44,700
the funeral of the late empress.

608
00:33:44,820 --> 00:33:46,260
No need to worry about it.

609
00:33:51,660 --> 00:33:54,380
Your Highness, if I may be so bold.

610
00:33:54,780 --> 00:33:56,380
Fu Yuan's identity is vague at best.

611
00:33:56,540 --> 00:33:59,340
Enthroning empress dowager
will affect the country.

612
00:33:59,540 --> 00:34:02,220
-Please reconsider.
-Insolent.

613
00:34:02,980 --> 00:34:04,900
Fu Yuan is my birth mother.

614
00:34:05,020 --> 00:34:06,820
She was the previous empress
of the last sovereign.

615
00:34:06,980 --> 00:34:08,500
How can her identity be vague?

616
00:34:08,700 --> 00:34:10,180
What objections do you have?

617
00:34:10,340 --> 00:34:14,060
Your Highness, Empress Fu has
passed away more than 10 years ago.

618
00:34:14,300 --> 00:34:17,020
We can't be sure of
this woman's background.

619
00:34:17,180 --> 00:34:20,260
And without proof, how can
she be the model for all woman?

620
00:34:20,420 --> 00:34:23,380
And how can she make
the people submit to her?

621
00:34:23,900 --> 00:34:24,980
Yang Wei.

622
00:34:25,740 --> 00:34:27,540
You've served the
late emperor for many years.

623
00:34:27,700 --> 00:34:30,780
Are you really unable to
recognise Empress Fu Yuan?

624
00:34:30,940 --> 00:34:33,660
His Highness,
I had served the late emperor.

625
00:34:33,860 --> 00:34:36,220
Of course I know about Empress Fu.

626
00:34:36,540 --> 00:34:38,740
And I know very well whether
or not she's qualified...

627
00:34:38,860 --> 00:34:41,180
to be the model for all women.

628
00:34:41,340 --> 00:34:43,940
So, no matter she is
Empress Fu or not,

629
00:34:44,140 --> 00:34:47,940
I won't allow her to be
empress dowager.

630
00:34:49,300 --> 00:34:50,860
Yang Wei.

631
00:34:51,380 --> 00:34:53,180
How dare you talk back
to your superior.

632
00:34:53,300 --> 00:34:55,980
I think you have had enough to be
the minister of Ministry of Rites.

633
00:34:56,140 --> 00:34:57,340
Even if...

634
00:34:57,460 --> 00:34:59,820
I'm not the minister of
this Ministry of Rites,

635
00:35:00,060 --> 00:35:03,940
I'll never recognise Fu Yuan
as empress dowager.

636
00:35:04,180 --> 00:35:05,260
Yang Wei!

637
00:35:07,380 --> 00:35:09,780
You are a senior official who had
served for more than 10 years.

638
00:35:09,940 --> 00:35:12,620
Among all the others here,
you should have known better!

639
00:35:12,900 --> 00:35:14,500
That day, in this very place,

640
00:35:14,820 --> 00:35:16,180
you had doubted my identity.

641
00:35:16,340 --> 00:35:17,540
Now,

642
00:35:17,740 --> 00:35:19,340
you want to do the same?

643
00:35:19,540 --> 00:35:22,220
You've defeated our enemy
and brought peace to the country.

644
00:35:22,380 --> 00:35:23,780
They are great merits.

645
00:35:23,940 --> 00:35:26,820
But if you enthroned her
as empress dowager,

646
00:35:27,020 --> 00:35:29,380
I'm afraid that from now on,
the court will be in chaos...

647
00:35:29,500 --> 00:35:30,940
and it'll be a disaster for
the country and the people.

648
00:35:31,060 --> 00:35:33,180
The merits that you've
achieved before this...

649
00:35:33,420 --> 00:35:35,140
will be gone in a split second.

650
00:35:35,260 --> 00:35:38,100
My mother is a weak lady.
How can she bring chaos to the court?

651
00:35:38,420 --> 00:35:40,460
Southern and northern regions
are all the same!

652
00:35:40,740 --> 00:35:43,460
Why do you have to condemn
such a weak lady?

653
00:35:43,740 --> 00:35:46,740
You just say that she'll endanger the
nation and accuse her for something.

654
00:35:47,020 --> 00:35:48,060
Her honour...

655
00:35:48,260 --> 00:35:50,860
is not something that others
can look down on easily.

656
00:35:51,340 --> 00:35:52,380
Guards!

657
00:35:55,220 --> 00:35:57,100
This...

658
00:35:58,100 --> 00:36:00,220
My fellow officials. Now,

659
00:36:00,660 --> 00:36:02,900
any of you still have objections?

660
00:36:17,460 --> 00:36:18,660
Your Highness.

661
00:36:18,860 --> 00:36:20,740
The coronation for empress dowager...

662
00:36:21,020 --> 00:36:23,740
is under the Ministry of Rite's duty.

663
00:36:24,260 --> 00:36:26,100
Other officials in this court...

664
00:36:26,260 --> 00:36:28,100
have nothing to do with it.

665
00:36:28,900 --> 00:36:30,940
If you insist on your decision...

666
00:36:31,140 --> 00:36:33,300
to enthrone Fu Yuan
as empress dowager,

667
00:36:33,500 --> 00:36:36,500
I'm willing to be punished
for being disrespectful.

668
00:36:36,660 --> 00:36:39,100
I'll retire and go back to
my hometown. From now on,

669
00:36:39,420 --> 00:36:42,420
please look for others
to take my place.

670
00:36:42,660 --> 00:36:44,220
Sir Yang.

671
00:36:44,460 --> 00:36:45,740
Sir Yang.

672
00:37:18,300 --> 00:37:20,500
We'll discuss about
the coronation of...

673
00:37:22,380 --> 00:37:23,940
empress dowager again next time.

674
00:37:29,900 --> 00:37:31,780
Your Highness, according to custom,

675
00:37:31,900 --> 00:37:34,180
late empress should be buried
together with the late emperor.

676
00:37:34,300 --> 00:37:36,660
But she is not given the title
as empress dowager yet.

677
00:37:36,860 --> 00:37:39,420
What kind of funeral
should we give her?

678
00:37:39,740 --> 00:37:42,020
How would I know about these
overelaborated formalities?

679
00:37:42,620 --> 00:37:44,220
By the way, remember...

680
00:37:44,780 --> 00:37:47,820
not to let anyone see
the looks of the late empress.

681
00:37:48,300 --> 00:37:49,580
I understand.

682
00:37:49,980 --> 00:37:51,740
How could a person
who's living well...

683
00:37:52,620 --> 00:37:54,580
commit suicide just like that?

684
00:37:58,380 --> 00:38:01,100
By the way,
don't tell mother about this.

685
00:38:01,300 --> 00:38:02,780
It'll only make her worry.

686
00:38:03,220 --> 00:38:05,420
Lately, she has recovered
from her illness even more.

687
00:38:05,540 --> 00:38:07,540
Arrival of Her Majesty!

688
00:38:13,300 --> 00:38:14,780
Greetings, mother.

689
00:38:18,540 --> 00:38:19,740
Chou.

690
00:38:20,980 --> 00:38:22,900
You have to take care of yourself.

691
00:38:23,220 --> 00:38:25,060
Health is more important.

692
00:38:25,780 --> 00:38:27,940
Thank you for your care.
I'll remember it.

693
00:38:28,180 --> 00:38:29,860
Mother, have a seat.

694
00:38:33,260 --> 00:38:34,620
Why do you...

695
00:38:35,180 --> 00:38:37,140
have so many reports today?

696
00:38:38,980 --> 00:38:40,340
Yang Wei...

697
00:38:40,580 --> 00:38:42,100
has left his post.

698
00:38:42,540 --> 00:38:43,820
After he left his post,

699
00:38:43,980 --> 00:38:46,340
Some of the vice ministers
from the Ministry of Rites...

700
00:38:46,540 --> 00:38:48,220
have quit their job as well.

701
00:38:48,500 --> 00:38:51,380
It's normal to have more work
when you have less people.

702
00:38:51,780 --> 00:38:52,940
It's not a big deal.

703
00:38:54,100 --> 00:38:56,100
-Chou.
-Mother.

704
00:38:58,940 --> 00:39:00,540
I won't blame Sir Yang...

705
00:39:01,060 --> 00:39:02,940
for what he did.

706
00:39:03,340 --> 00:39:06,580
He's just being more cautious
because this concerns...

707
00:39:06,900 --> 00:39:08,380
the benefit of the nation.

708
00:39:08,980 --> 00:39:12,500
If you want to hire him
to work for the court again,

709
00:39:12,780 --> 00:39:14,940
I won't mind it as well.

710
00:39:15,700 --> 00:39:17,500
I know Yang Wei quite well.

711
00:39:17,740 --> 00:39:19,780
With his temper by nature,
since he has left,

712
00:39:20,100 --> 00:39:21,540
he won't be coming back anymore.

713
00:39:24,380 --> 00:39:25,580
Mother.

714
00:39:27,260 --> 00:39:28,660
I've been...

715
00:39:28,980 --> 00:39:31,420
delaying your coronation
again and again.

716
00:39:31,780 --> 00:39:33,340
Do you really don't mind about it?

717
00:39:34,820 --> 00:39:37,300
You said it many times.

718
00:39:37,860 --> 00:39:40,700
I know. You have
no choice but to do it...

719
00:39:40,860 --> 00:39:43,780
because of the current situation.

720
00:39:44,060 --> 00:39:45,780
Thank you for your
understanding, mother.

721
00:39:46,780 --> 00:39:49,580
Somebody lacks judgement.

722
00:39:49,900 --> 00:39:53,020
If they want to leave,
let them go then.

723
00:39:53,980 --> 00:39:56,740
No need to rack your brains for it.

724
00:40:02,100 --> 00:40:03,300
Mother.

725
00:40:03,700 --> 00:40:05,300
You don't understand.

726
00:40:07,020 --> 00:40:09,900
All the officials in this court...

727
00:40:10,380 --> 00:40:12,140
have stayed behind...

728
00:40:13,140 --> 00:40:15,380
not because they are willing
to serve me wholeheartedly.

729
00:40:16,140 --> 00:40:19,020
They did it for the benefit
of Northern Realm only.

730
00:40:19,780 --> 00:40:22,060
After this coronation incident,

731
00:40:22,300 --> 00:40:23,980
I can see it even clearer now.

732
00:40:24,940 --> 00:40:28,300
Although I've been ruling
Northern Realm for more than a year,

733
00:40:29,020 --> 00:40:30,620
these officials...

734
00:40:31,620 --> 00:40:33,820
still haven't submit themselves
completely to me.

735
00:40:34,580 --> 00:40:37,300
I have my Armour Army to force them.

736
00:40:37,500 --> 00:40:38,620
But...

737
00:40:39,300 --> 00:40:42,140
it's not enough to suppress
the arrogance in them.

738
00:40:42,420 --> 00:40:43,740
That is because...

739
00:40:44,140 --> 00:40:45,820
you are not ruthless enough.

740
00:40:46,660 --> 00:40:49,460
Chou, as the ruler of the country,

741
00:40:49,660 --> 00:40:52,060
you are too soft-hearted.

742
00:40:53,900 --> 00:40:55,100
Mother.

743
00:40:56,700 --> 00:40:58,340
Making them submit by force...

744
00:40:58,860 --> 00:41:00,620
is of the worst plan.

745
00:41:01,540 --> 00:41:04,380
Although I can't say that
I'll be a sage,

746
00:41:05,660 --> 00:41:08,220
I don't want to be a tyrant as well.
